      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people want to help but it doesnt change the reality. it doesn't change the fact that i have nothing left to offer. i've spent every waking hour on this and now there's just this massive void. i'm just so incredibly drained. i feel like i'm just running in place in a dark room and i'm too tired to even keep walking. i just want the noise to stop. i just want everything to be quiet.",
